[Gonaives is the major city of the Artibonite valley where the outbreak
began. The overall morbidity and mortality numbers continue to rise and the
epidemic continues to spread. - Mod.LL

A continually updated interactive map of the cholera situation in Haiti is
available from HealthMap at <http://www.healthmap.org/haiti/>. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
